{"tid":1559786,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"屢撐抗爭 Shine疑拆夥 天佑fb留言暫別 自稱四面受敵","createTime":"2019-09-11T03:14:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-11T14:46:03.000Z","uid":25558,"like":31,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"adebdc6946605a885bc872ca8118c4cee4f2c51e","tid":1559786,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T03:14:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20190911/20765791\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190911%2F20765791&d=3A5iQKMTOMHlOvaIjHeReswCZVYJieBIKSEfzXA%2FSmA%3D&h=f383405a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190911%2F20765791&h=6eee25ca\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20190911/20765791</a><br />\n<br />\n屢撐抗爭 Shine疑拆夥<br />\n天佑fb留言暫別 自稱四面受敵<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190911/large/1568118432_72b7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190911%2Flarge%2F1568118432_72b7.jpg&h=3e5ecc77&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n徐天佑連月來一直支持抗爭運動，為年輕人發聲。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n逆權運動以來，組合Shine的徐天佑不斷在facebook出帖文，支持敢於抗爭的香港人，亦寫了新歌《不只你一個》與年輕人同行。由6.12衝擊立法會開始，徐天佑於facebook更換「黑頭像」，留言支持抗爭運動，獲不少網民支持，但亦有網民肆意攻擊他，不過，連月來他仍不間斷為香港人、年輕人加油，近日更有人以天佑在《那夜凌晨，我坐上了旺角開往大埔的紅VAN》中的經典對白「大家不要再欺騙自己說，外面一切都是正常的。」形容香港現狀。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190911/large/1568118431_790e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190911%2Flarge%2F1568118431_790e.jpg&h=30d3c605&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n天佑的留言語帶無奈，聲稱「暫別」的他似受壓被滅聲。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190911/large/1568118431_6e8c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190911%2Flarge%2F1568118431_6e8c.jpg&h=2fc2d49c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2002年徐天佑與黃又南組成Shine，之後曾分開發展，2012年重組，去年3月曾舉行演唱會。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n網民留言撐到底<br />\n<br />\n天佑前晚在facebook再出帖文，留言會與香港人齊上齊落、不割席。被問到「Shine是否都齊上齊落？」時，他回覆：「no more shine.」其後天佑再度開post：「壞人當道。我係一個好人，如果我瀨嘢，希望你會相信我係一個好人。」又留下一句：「暫別。」令人懷疑Shine似拆夥，很多人隨即留言支持撐到底。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n矛頭直指黃又南<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》前晚聯絡天佑，他以WhatsApp回覆說：「Sorry，四面受敵。I can't say anything。」他又指壓力很大：「一言難盡，估唔到會係咁。」至於Shine經理人錢小姐回覆《蘋果》時否認二人拆夥：「佢哋冇拆夥，感情冇問題，各自拍戲。所以先冇時間一齊工作，如果之後有演唱會，都可以再一齊。」<br />\n<br />\n其實這次疑似拆夥早有端倪，天佑7月時開post說過：「現在社會，發聲是錯？有好多人因此割席我不管，有『人』同我講『不如你唔好再講嘢啦』，我明白&hellip;&hellip;但可以嗎？低頭嗎？被滅聲的感覺很微妙，亦很壯麗。你看今天的集會舒服嗎？我不會，香港加油！」直至8月4日，他又有感而發，於社交網留言︰「我感謝一啲『真』朋友，打俾我Message我鼓勵我支持我&hellip;&hellip;BTW成日稱兄道弟嗰啲割席嗰啲，我唔會阻你哋搵食。」他口中「稱兄道弟嗰啲」、「割席嗰啲」，矛頭直指Shine的黃又南。<br />\n<br />\n撰文︰祖李 <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n黃嘉雯笑對情史曝光<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n【馮仁昭四圍超】一手創造林亞珍 名製作人陳家蓀病逝"},{"pid":"128d4a5d5b0106b6de41795b6a294caac7381093","tid":1559786,"uid":38904,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T03:16:20.000Z","msg":"良心歌手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e7e0ef90a8f5e972ddd04122eedbd7c7cbffadf","tid":1559786,"uid":27064,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T03:17:17.000Z","msg":"天佑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a16f93fec42d50a3bdbbb9dbaaf7481f95202ed0","tid":1559786,"uid":260036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T03:18:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jpUx0Hn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjpUx0Hn.jpg&h=994192ea&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"40243f